{"id":558621,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/水军不够-法官来凑：抚顺法官微博匿名攻击迟夙生/","date":"2017-05-10T07:54:08Z","modified":"2017-05-10T08:06:28Z","title":"【立此存照】水军不够 法官来凑：抚顺法官匿名攻击迟夙生","content":"<p>2017年5月9日上午，夙生律师事务所在微博曝光，称年近六旬的迟夙生律师在抚顺市望花区法院庭审过程中，遭到该院粗暴对待，在晕倒后仍被法警一路拖拽下楼梯，后被送至医院接受治疗。@夙生律师事务所 的相关微博目前已被和谐。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558638\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/夙生律师事务所微博.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-558638\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/夙生律师事务所微博.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/夙生律师事务所微博.png 1206w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/夙生律师事务所微博-260x300.png 260w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/夙生律师事务所微博-768x885.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/夙生律师事务所微博-888x1024.png 888w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@夙生律师事务所 微博截图；现已被和谐</span></p></div>\n<p>抚顺市望花区法院官方微博于当天晚18时发布了<a href=\"http://weibo.com/3650619397/F2kFM6z3Z\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">回应</a>，称当时是阻止迟夙生律师对庭审直播，但迟拒绝并“大吵大闹”，整个过程中“法警未有任何拉拽和过激动作”。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558637\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院微博.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-558637\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院微博.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"652\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院微博.png 1206w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院微博-230x300.png 230w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院微博-768x1001.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院微博-786x1024.png 786w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@辽宁省抚顺市望花区法院 微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>当天晚20时45分，抚顺市望花区法院官博发布了一条配有迟夙生律师照片的微博，借其曾建议卖淫合法化来攻击迟律师，暗示她不可靠。在引来大量批评后，望花区法院删除了这条微博。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558660\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/4bdb1fa0ly1fffgfyy1wuj20k00zkgp1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558660\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/4bdb1fa0ly1fffgfyy1wuj20k00zkgp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/4bdb1fa0ly1fffgfyy1wuj20k00zkgp1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/4bdb1fa0ly1fffgfyy1wuj20k00zkgp1-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/4bdb1fa0ly1fffgfyy1wuj20k00zkgp1-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">被删微博截图 via @周泽律师</span></p></div>\n<p>不过，在该院针对迟律师事件的情况说明下，得赞数最高的评论与上述攻击迟夙生律师的微博内容基本一致：</p>\n<blockquote><p>@壹伍玖一一一：这个律师太有名了，曾提过卖淫合法化的是不是此人哪？</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_558634\" style=\"width: 585px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院宋茹萱01.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558634\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院宋茹萱01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院宋茹萱01.jpg 1216w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院宋茹萱01-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院宋茹萱01-768x441.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/抚顺市望花区法院宋茹萱01-1024x588.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@辽宁省抚顺市望花区法院 微博热评截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>经中国数字时代编辑检索发现，这位匿名攻击迟夙生的 @壹伍玖一一一，其实就是抚顺市望花区法院法官、<a href=\"http://www.weirz.com/thread-7312-1-1.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">团委书记</a>宋茹萱。</strong></p>\n<p>宋茹萱虽然已删除绝大部分的微博内容，但她的个性域名“songruxuan”已无法改变：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558630\" style=\"width: 585px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558630\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02.jpg 1676w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02-300x194.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02-768x497.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02-1024x662.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱02-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@壹伍玖一一一 主页截图</span></p></div>\n<p>她2011年的微博照片水印显示，个性域名“songruxuan”即“宋茹萱”：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558632\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱03.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558632\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱03.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"516\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱03.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱03-233x300.jpg 233w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱03-768x990.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱03-794x1024.jpg 794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博用户 @壹伍玖一一一 改名前的发布的图片，显示其为宋茹萱</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_558643\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558643\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱4.jpg 2026w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱4-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱4-768x446.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/宋茹萱4-1024x594.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">抚顺市望花区法院官网截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>附 @夙生律师事务所 被删微博图片：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1fffx8wjgrxj20ku112te7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558636\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1fffx8wjgrxj20ku112te7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1fffx8wjgrxj20ku112te7.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1fffx8wjgrxj20ku112te7-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1fffx8wjgrxj20ku112te7-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyflj0l2j20zk0qo40h.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558645\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyflj0l2j20zk0qo40h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyflj0l2j20zk0qo40h.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyflj0l2j20zk0qo40h-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfmjtasj20qo0zkacl.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558646\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfmjtasj20qo0zkacl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfmjtasj20qo0zkacl.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfmjtasj20qo0zkacl-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfp56czj20qo0zkjth.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558647\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfp56czj20qo0zkjth.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfp56czj20qo0zkjth.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfp56czj20qo0zkjth-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfpuotqj20k00zk3zz.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558648\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfpuotqj20k00zk3zz.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfpuotqj20k00zk3zz.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfpuotqj20k00zk3zz-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfpuotqj20k00zk3zz-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfrpoqmj20k00zk40h.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-558649\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfrpoqmj20k00zk40h.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfrpoqmj20k00zk40h.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfrpoqmj20k00zk40h-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/74e335a5ly1ffeyfrpoqmj20k00zk40h-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9239,25313,11848,9378,32760]}